[deckList.js]  --> displays all decks --> Study --> [deckDetail.js]
                                      --> Edit  --> [editDeck.js]
                                      --> Export/Download JSON
                                      --> Delete

[flashcard.js] --> Create new deck --> Save --> [storage.js] --> deckList.js

[library.js]   --> Show library decks --> Add deck --> [storage.js] --> deckList.js

[faq.js]       --> Toggle FAQ questions (UI only)


----->storage.js is the central hub for all deck CRUD operations
----->deckList.js is the main hub / dashboard
----->flashcard.js and editDeck.js are forms for creating or editing decks
----->deckDetail.js is the interactive study view
----->library.js is optional for importing decks
----->faq.js is UI enhancement